text: Sector Seven, Sector 7, or variations thereon may refer to: * Sector 7 (book), a wordless picture book created and illustrated by David Wiesner * Sector 7 (film), a 2011 South Korean 3D science fiction action film directed by Kim Ji- hoon * Sector 7, one of eleven geographical areas of Bangladesh during the Bangladesh Liberation War * Sector Seven, a fictional US government agency in the 2007 film Transformers * Sectorseven, a Canadian punk band from in Grimsby, Ontario * Sectorseven (album), the third studio album by Sector Seven == See also == * Area 7 (disambiguation) * District 7 (disambiguation)
